name: NOUNDO.
description:
The undo operation is going back to a previous state. Is something of computers, but not real life. 

Done in PaintingVR very hungry, a pretty cool canvas drawing VR app, where you can not make an undo, so mistake in a stroke, you die. Edited with Pixlr without any undo as well.

In a virtual world, I want the freedom to be able to be wrong, please PaintingVR support the undo and make feel awesome with your app!
